# How It Works

1. User types into the input bar.
2. JavaScript detects the input.
3. A request is sent to GitHub's API.
4. Repository results are returned.
5. Results appear in the dropdown.
6. User clicks a result to open GitHub.

---

# GitHub API

This project uses:

```
https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q={query}
```

Documentation:

```
https://docs.github.com/en/rest/search/search
```

